high_descs: Turn left and walk to the white table in front of you.
Pick up the spoon that's in front of you.
Turn around and take two steps then turn left and walk to the sink.
Wash the spoon in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Turn around and take a step then turn right and walk to the white table then turn right.
Put the spoon to the right of the bowl on the black table so it's laying vertically near the right corner on the edge.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spoon on the table.

high_descs: walk to face white rectangular table
wash spoon in sink, pick up spoon from sink
move slightly left to face black shelves left of the sink
put spoon onto black shelves to the right of the brown bowl
anns.task_desc: put a washed spoon onto shelves

high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the white table.
Pick up the metal spoon off of the table.
Turn around and walk towards the wall, then turn left and walk up to the sink.
Put the metal spoon in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean spoon.
Turn around and walk towards the wall, then hang a right and walk up to the white table, after that turn right to face the black shelving unit.
Put the clean metal spoon on the front right corner of the top of the black shelving unit.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spoon on a black shelving unit.
